?p=305081\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:565:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Premium WooCommerce Template Builder brings the power of Page Builder to WooCommerce. Version <code>1.21.0</code> introduces a new template and widgets to customize the WooCommerce Thank You page. The Thank You page follows checking out and provides users with an order status, summary, and other information.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/customize-the-woocommerce-thank-you-page/\">Customize the WooCommerce Thank You Page</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2903:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Premium WooCommerce Template Builder brings the power of Page Builder to WooCommerce. Version <code>1.21.0</code> introduces a new template and widgets to customize the WooCommerce Thank You page. The Thank You page follows checking out and provides users with an order status, summary, and other information.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_305097\" style=\"width: 1210px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-305097\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/thank-you-default.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" class=\"size-full wp-image-305097\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/thank-you-default.jpg 1200w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/thank-you-default-300x225.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/thank-you-default-699x524.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/thank-you-default-768x576.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/thank-you-default-1050x788.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/thank-you-default-313x235.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-305097\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">WooCommerce Thank You Page</p></div>\n<p>While any number of widgets can be used in the Thank You template, the following new widgets have been added to provide template-specific functionality:</p>\n<p><strong>Thank you order status:</strong> Displays the order status. Use this widget to edit the success and failure messages as required.<br />\n<strong>Thank you order overview:</strong> Display an overview of the order.<br />\n<strong>Thank you order details:</strong> Displays a table of order details.<br />\n<strong>Thank you order downloads:</strong> Displays order downloads.<br />\n<strong>Thank you customer details:</strong> Displays customer details.</p>\n<p>Two template ideas we have logged for the future are:</p>\n<p><strong>Custom coupon widget:</strong><br />\nGenerate a unique coupon for the user after purchase.</p>\n<p><strong>Product/category specific Thank You templates:</strong><br />\nCustom Thank You pages based on specific products or categories of products purchased.</p>\n<p>Are there any template-specific widgets or functionality you&#8217;d like to see added to this template? Let us know in the comments below.</p>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/woocommerce-templates/\">SiteOrigin Premium WooCommerce Template Builder documentation</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">Find out more about SiteOrigin Premium</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/customize-the-woocommerce-thank-you-page/\">Customize the WooCommerce Thank You Page</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://siteorigin.com/customize-the-woocommerce-thank-you-page/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"Post Carousel: New Design and Responsive Settings\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://siteorigin.com/post-carousel-new-design-and-responsive-settings/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"https://siteorigin.com/post-carousel-new-design-and-responsive-settings/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 21 Mar 2021 14:42:39 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=300301\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:496:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle version <code>1.17.0</code> migrated the Post Carousel widget from in-house JavaScript to the Slick carousel library. Since then we’ve added a series of useful new settings and features you may have missed.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/post-carousel-new-design-and-responsive-settings/\">Post Carousel: New Design and Responsive Settings</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3714:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle version <code>1.17.0</code> migrated the Post Carousel widget from in-house JavaScript to the Slick carousel library. Since then we&#8217;ve added a series of new settings and features you may have missed.</p>\n<h3>New Settings</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Added a <strong>Link target</strong> to setting. Choose to open links in the current or a new tab.</li>\n<li>Added a new <strong>Design</strong> settings section which includes the following:\n<ul>\n<li>Thumbnail overlay hover color</li>\n<li>Thumbnail overlay hover opacity</li>\n<li>Navigation arrow color</li>\n<li>Navigation arrow hover color</li>\n<li>Navigation background</li>\n<li>Navigation hover background</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Added a <strong>Responsive</strong> settings section. Change the <strong>Slides to scroll</strong> for desktop, tablet and mobile as well as the device resolutions for each.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>New Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Added right to left language support</li>\n<li>Improved support for multiple carousel widgets on the same page.</li>\n<li>Improved mobile device support. Swiping to view more posts is now easier.</li>\n<li>Added a filter to restrict the total number of posts loaded <code>siteorigin_widgets_post_carousel_post_limit</code>.\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_299816\" style=\"width: 1968px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-299816\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/post-carousel-widget-settings.jpg\" alt=\"SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget Settings\" width=\"1958\" height=\"1268\" class=\"size-full wp-image-299816\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/post-carousel-widget-settings.jpg 1958w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/post-carousel-widget-settings-300x194.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/post-carousel-widget-settings-699x453.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/post-carousel-widget-settings-768x497.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/post-carousel-widget-settings-1536x995.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/post-carousel-widget-settings-1050x680.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/post-carousel-widget-settings-313x203.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1958px) 100vw, 1958px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-299816\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Post Carousel Widget Settings</p></div>\n<p>We hope you&#8217;re enjoying and making use of the new Post Carousel settings and features. If there is anything you&#8217;d like to see added to the Post Carousel in the future, please, let us know in the comments below.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/#blog\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">View a Post Carousel demo</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/post-carousel-widget/\">View the Post Carousel documentation</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/so-widgets-bundle/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Download the SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle plugin</a>.</p>\n<h3>Enhanced by SiteOrigin Premium</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">SiteOrigin Premium</a> offers a huge array of additional functionality for the SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle, Page Builder by SiteOrigin, SiteOrigin CSS, and all of our themes. SiteOrigin Premium also includes access to our next-level email support service, perfect for those times when you need fast and effective technical support.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/post-carousel-new-design-and-responsive-settings/\">Post Carousel: New Design and Responsive Settings</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://siteorigin.com/post-carousel-new-design-and-responsive-settings/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n				