ofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/insert-mirror-widgets-using-shortcodes/\">Insert Mirror Widgets Using Shortcodes</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3376:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Premium Mirror Widgets addon allows you to create a widget once and use it everywhere. When the Mirror Widget is updated, changes reflect in all instances of the widget.</p>\n<p>Mirror Widgets can be inserted into any Page Builder page or widget sidebar area using the dedicated widget.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_176845\" style=\"width: 1832px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-176845\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-176845 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1822\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget.png 1822w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-300x64.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-768x164.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-699x150.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-1050x225.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-313x67.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1822px) 100vw, 1822px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-176845\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Add Mirror Widgets to a page or theme sidebar area using the dedicated widget.</p></div>\n<p>SiteOrigin Premium version <code>1.19.0</code> adds the ability to insert Mirror Widgets using a shortcode. Mirror Widget shortcodes can be inserted into <strong>any page, post, or widget</strong> allowing for greater content management flexibility. Widgets that support shortcodes include the SiteOrigin Editor, Features, and Price Table to name a few.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_297739\" style=\"width: 1646px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-297739\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1636\" height=\"667\" class=\"size-full wp-image-297739\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode.jpg 1636w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-300x122.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-699x285.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-768x313.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-1536x626.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-1050x428.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-313x128.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1636px) 100vw, 1636px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-297739\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mirror Widgets shortcodes are available in the archive and single post view.</p></div>\n<p>Already using SiteOrigin Premium? Find out more about using the Mirror Widgets addon in the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/mirror-widgets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">premium documentation</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/insert-mirror-widgets-using-shortcodes/\">Insert Mirror Widgets Using Shortcodes</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://siteorigin.com/insert-mirror-widgets-using-shortcodes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Google Maps Consent Prompt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://siteorigin.com/google-maps-consent-prompt/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://siteorigin.com/google-maps-consent-prompt/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 23 Feb 2021 21:25:34 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=295597\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:549:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle version <code>1.17.9</code> adds a consent prompt option to the Google Maps widget. User consent is required before loading the Google Maps API for sites complying with regulations like DSGVO, or GDPR. The consent prompt settings are located at Plugins &#62; SiteOrigin Widgets &#62; Google Maps: Settings.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/google-maps-consent-prompt/\">Google Maps Consent Prompt</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4430:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle version <code>1.17.9</code> adds a consent prompt option to the Google Maps widget. User consent is required before loading the Google Maps API for sites complying with regulations like DSGVO, or GDPR. Once the consent prompt setting is enabled, no connection will be made to Google&#8217;s servers until after the user consents. The consent prompt settings are located at <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Widgets</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Google Maps: Settings</span></span>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/google-maps-api-consent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">View a demo</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_295602\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-295602\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-295602 size-large\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-699x628.jpg\" alt=\"Google Maps Widget API Consent Settings\" width=\"699\" height=\"628\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-699x628.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-300x270.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-768x690.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-1050x943.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings-313x281.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-widget-api-consent-settings.jpg 1476w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-295602\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Google Maps Widget API Consent Settings</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/google-maps-widget/#heading-global-settings\">Google Maps Widget Consent Prompt Documentation</a></p>\n<h3>Enhanced by SiteOrigin Premium</h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/?featured_addon=plugin/map-styles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SiteOrigin Premium Map Styles</a> addon provides three additional settings:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Consent prompt text color.</li>\n<li>Consent prompt text background color.</li>\n<li>Consent prompt background image.</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_295599\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-295599\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-699x584.jpg\" alt=\"oogle Maps API Consent Settings\" width=\"699\" height=\"584\" class=\"size-large wp-image-295599\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-699x584.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-300x251.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-768x642.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-1050x877.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings-313x262.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/google-maps-consent-prompt-settings.jpg 1448w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-295599\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Consent Prompt Design Settings</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/map-styles/#heading-google-maps-api-consent-additional-settings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SiteOrigin Premium Google Maps API Consent Additional Settings Documentation</a></p>\n<p>SiteOrigin Premium offers a huge array of additional functionality for Page Builder by SiteOrigin, the SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle, SiteOrigin CSS, and all of our themes. SiteOrigin Premium also includes access to our next-level email support service, perfect for those times when you need fast and effective technical support.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/google-maps-consent-prompt/\">Google Maps Consent Prompt</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml